title: Friend Roulette "Rocket Dog": Converse Rubber Tracks
description:
Check out the original music video created by Alexander Hunter and Nicolas Cadena for Friend Roulette, who recorded their song "Rocket Dog" at Converse Rubber Tracks studio. 

Converse's A/V Connection project pairs artists and filmmakers together to collaborate on music videos for tracks recorded at the Converse Rubber Tracks Studio.

Directors: Alexander Hunter and Nicolas Cadena
Producer: Grace Na
Director of Photography: Renee Mao
Production Designer: Violet Overn
Editors: Grace Na, Nicolas Cadena, and Alexander Hunter
First Assistant Director: Mary Kerrigan
Second Assistant Director: Matthew Puccini
Gaffer: Daniel Stenzel
First Assistant Camera (Day 1): Jesse Rosenberg
First Assistant Camera (Days 2 & 3): Ahad Mahmood
Second Assistant Camera: Skyler Johnson
Steadicam Operator: Patrick Morgan
Construction Manager: Camilo Cadena 
Art Director: Mary Hodge
Art Assistant: Andrea Massaad
Art Assistant: Zoë Hoetzel
Key Grip (Day 1): Nicco Quinones
Key Grip (Days 2 & 3): Zach Romeo
Color Grader: Grace Na

Starring: 
Julia Tepper
Duncan Bindbeutel
Liz Chuday
Kylie Garcelon
Robert Braxton
Sally Pospischil
Eve Sorel
Steve Garfanti
Matt Meade


Special Thanks To: Michael Overn, Ben Dewey

Produced by Friend Roulette and Jason Finkel

Recorded and mixed by Jason Finkel
Assisted by Aaron Bastinelli
